  {
    "id": "2651287713_3",
    "title": "内核级的真相：为什么 eBPF 正在取代基于用户空间的 Agent 成为安全可观测性的首选",
    "link": "http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651287713&idx=3&sn=7e2457fe3e33f8e4dd4b682b10fc5d0b&chksm=bdba88f28acd01e4c979104cd0275b94811afcbed36bc9cc487c7a41a3d278bb7fc63be4d0c9#rd",
    "publishTime": 1782376598,
